The invention relates to an online repair method aimed at a file system, and belongs to the technical field of computer storage. The online repair method comprises the following steps: scanning the damage of a storage volume associated with the file system, carrying out real-time error correction, and simultaneously keeping the storage volume online, so that the file system still can respond to an IO request; during the scanning process, classifying encountering errors, and adopting a corresponding repair scheme; during the repair process, establishing repair time for specific errors, and giving out a repair rate of progress; if the repair is in failure, clearing off the data; Establishing a manager device above the storage volume, and taking the last part of storage space of the storage volume as a logger device, wherein the manager device is in charge of management and maintenance; during the period of error amending, intercepting and processing the IO request issued by the file system by the manager device; processing a read-write request aimed at the damaged part of the storage volume. According to the online repair method, during the period of repairing the errors of the storage volume, the file system still can respond to the IO request normally.
